Ready?

35
00:01:56,826 --> 00:01:58,953
No mercy! No mercy!

36
00:01:59,162 --> 00:02:00,830
Weigh the fist, Johnny.

37
00:02:00,914 --> 00:02:02,332
Finish him!

38
00:02:11,758 --> 00:02:13,009
Winner!

39
00:02:21,518 --> 00:02:22,852
Now who's the loser?

40
00:02:22,936 --> 00:02:24,687
You're really sick, man.

41
00:02:24,813 --> 00:02:26,981
How does second place feel now?

42
00:02:27,065 --> 00:02:29,109
- He can't breathe.
- Mind your business.

43
00:02:29,192 --> 00:02:32,529
- You're gonna kill him.
- <i>Sensei</i>, please. You're hurting him.

44
00:02:32,612 --> 00:02:34,823
He's sorry, okay? He really is.

45
00:02:36,324 --> 00:02:37,408
Let him go.

46
00:02:37,492 --> 00:02:39,619
Beat it, slope, or you're next.

47
